column2: SELECT TOP # G.ra,G.dec,G.modelMag_r,G.modelMagErr_r,G.extinction_r, pz.z,pz.zErr, G.modelFlux_u, G.modelFlux_g,  G.modelFlux_r, G.modelFlux_i FROM dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) AS GN JOIN Galaxy AS G ON GN.objID = G.objID JOIN PhotoTag AS pt ON pt.objID = G.objID JOIN Photoz AS pz ON GN.objID = pz.objID ORDER by distance
